  <h1 class="center" style="text-align: center">Reconfigurable Intelligent Systems Engineering Laboratory</h1>
  <p>R.I.S.E. Group is a research group in the CSE Dept. of IIT Madras working in the areas of Computer Architecture, Security,
    Machine Learning and VLSI Design. If you wish to collaborate with us, please contact the relevant Faculty members from
    the People's page.
  </p>
  <p>The RISE group of laboratories was started in 2002, with an aim to focus on reconfigurable computing systems and artificial
    intelligence. Over the years RISE has played host to 7 faculties, over 100+ research scholars and nearly 500 undergraduate
    students.
  </p>
  <p> The Rise group of laboratories consists of 4 labs namely
    <ul>
      <li>Interactive Intelligence Laboratory</li>
      <li>Computer Architecture and System Design Laboratory</li>
      <li>The indeginous microprocessor development (SHAKTI) Laboratory</li>
      <li>The Secure Systems Group</li>
    </ul>
  </p>
